# Drowsiness Detection System 🚗💤

## 📌 Overview
This project detects drowsiness using MPU6050 sensor and alerts using LEDs and buzzer.

## ⚙️ Hardware
- Arduino Nano
- MPU6050
- LEDs
- Buzzer

## 💻 Software
- Arduino IDE
- Python (Serial Monitoring)

## 🔌 Working
- Arduino reads sensor data
- Sends data via Serial
- Python analyzes data
- LED + Buzzer alerts

## ▶️ How to Run

### Arduino
Upload code using Arduino IDE

### Python
Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt

Run:
python detection.py

